# A mexican dish made by filling a [[tortilla]] (corn or flour) with cheese, folding in half and toasting until the cheese is melted.  Additional ingredients, such as meats (chicken or beef, commonly), or vegetables can be added.  <s>Always</s> <u>Often</u> served with salsa, guacamole and/or sour cream.

